{"tid":628694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 工作壓力爆煲　男子祥華邨墮樓命危","createTime":"2018-04-14T05:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:03:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"beeb729a5910ee25250ea676c50cadc7a4bcc8d9","tid":628694,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"粉嶺發生墮樓事件，昨(13日)晚11時許，一名33歲姓葉男子，被人發現倒臥祥華邨祥禮樓附近停車場對開空地，葉男清醒由救護員送往沙田威爾斯醫院救治，目前情況危殆。警方到場調查，在地上發現小量血漬及一張染血紙巾，估計事主從2樓梯間墮下，現場未有檢獲遺書。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，葉近日<span style=\"color: red;\">因工作問題不開心</span>，懷疑因此輕生，事件沒有可疑，警方將案件列企圖自殺<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180414/bkn-20180414001152888-0414_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180414%2Fbkn-20180414001152888-0414_00822_001.html&d=WxIVqh6e2MKgQ83lfIU2XMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=edd12a6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180414/bkn-20180414001152888-0414_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"65961a4332e3a54d8d12e4c3e94a0366f2b8b4ff","tid":628694,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"none care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}